                     <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xfa="http://www.xfa.org/schema/xfa-data/1.0/"><p style="letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">            </span><span style="xfa-tab-count:3">                           </span><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">         </span><span style="font-size:8pt">Net Weight<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">     </span>:<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">  </span></span><span style="font-size:8pt"><span xfa:embed="#floatingField009894" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></span></p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in">I/E CODE : 3105018760<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">        </span><span style="xfa-tab-count:1">         </span><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">           </span>Gross Weight :<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">  </span><span xfa:embed="#floatingField028703" xfa:embedMode="raw" xfa:embedType="uri"/></p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span></p><p style="font-size:8pt;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0in">Declaration:</p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in">1. Goods not used after manufacturing</p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in">2. We declare that this invoice shows the actual price of the goods described</p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">    </span>and that all particulars are true and correct.</p></body>
                  </exData>
